high_descs: Turn left then cross the room turn left walk forward then turn right by the window
Pick up the watering can on the wall
Turn left then cross the room head to the tv stand
Put the watering can in front of the tv on the tv stand
anns.task_desc: Put the watering can in front of the tv on the tv stand

high_descs: Turn left and walk until you're almost to the end of the green striped rug but turn left before you are and walk to the black table then turn right and walk to the wall then turn left.
Pick up the watering can that's in front of you on the floor.
Walk back to where you started but walk to the tv before you get there and stand in front of it.
Put the watering can in front of the tv's base on top of the top left corner of the newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Put a watering can on the tv stand.

high_descs: Turn left, go towards the fireplace, turn left, go across the room and then turn right and go to the window.
Pick up the tea pot on the floor.
Head back to the fire place, turn right and go to the dresser with the TV on it.
Put the tea pot on the dresser to the left of the newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Put a tea pot on the dresser.
